  <p>Creates a new <link xref="GLib.Error"/>; unlike <link xref="GLib.new"/>, <code>message</code> is
not a printf()-style format string. Use this function if
<code>message</code> contains text you don't have control over,
that could include printf() escape sequences.</p>

